                  <triggerstring n="impl_rules">und sind zu beczalen von den nagstkunftigen ostern uber
                     funf gancze jar, die darnach nagstnacheinander komend an alles vertziehen, ut
                     littera sonat</triggerstring>. <date>Actum an Mitichen vor dem Suntag Letare in
                     der vasten, anno etc. l<hi rend="super">mo</hi></date>.</rs></p><p rend="Summa">Summa iii tl., v s. xviii d.</p></div><div type="lists"><xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../../../../indices/placeList.xml" xpointer="element(/1/2/1/1)"/><xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../../../../indices/personList.xml" xpointer="element(/1/2/1/1)"/><xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../../../../indices/eventList.xml" xpointer="element(/1/2/1/1)"/><xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../../../../indices/orgList.xml" xpointer="element(/1/2/1/1)"/></div></body></text></TEI>